{"html":"<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.s{width:1080px;height:1350px;background:#0A0A0A;position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;padding:90px 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;color:#fff}.top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}.logo{height:42px;filter:brightness(0) invert(1)}.num{font-family:'Anton',sans-serif;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:4px;color:#F4C000}.err{font-family:'Anton',sans-serif;font-size:240px;line-height:1;color:#F4C000;margin-bottom:-30px}.label{font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:6px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px;color:#F4C000}h1{font-family:'Anton',sans-serif;font-size:96px;line-height:0.95;text-transform:uppercase}p{margin-top:36px;font-size:26px;line-height:1.45;max-width:880px;color:#e5e5e5}.rule{width:80px;height:3px;background:#F4C000;margin-top:40px}.foot{font-size:15px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;color:#F4C000}</style><div class=\"s\"><div class=\"top\"><img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\"><div class=\"num\">03 / 06</div></div><div><div class=\"err\">#02</div><div class=\"label\">Error de uso</div><h1>Dejarla siempre enchufada</h1><p>Mantenerla 24/7 conectada al cargador degrada la batería. Permití que baje y vuelva a cargar para alargar su vida útil.</p><div class=\"rule\"></div></div><div class=\"foot\">Pc Clean</div></div>"}
